OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA blustery day, with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, which could be
OL,7,Fheavy at times. A few bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells possible, mainly during the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,12,Fon Saturday, with showers and perhaps
OL,13,Fsome longer spells of rain. Bright and
OL,14,Fbreezy on Easter Sunday, with a
OL,15,Fscattering of showers. Drier and
OL,16,Fwarmer for Easter Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
